                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281023-137-off813 t18281023-137-crimeloc815"></join>. On the 24th of September, about two o'clock, I saw Riley take a glass basin from the table in the shop - there is no window - he took it without going in; he went on and gave it to Moore, who put it under his jacket; Riley then ran on and Moore went after him, but not so fast; I told Howard of it - he went and brought back Moore with the basin; Riley was not taken till past eleven o'clock at night; I had seen him about for two or three days.</p>
